Vitol is an energy and commodities company.
Every day we use our expertise and logistical networks to distribute energy around the world, efficiently and responsibly. Founded in Rotterdam in 1966, today the company has some 40 offices worldwide and trades over seven million barrels of crude oil and products a day. What we do










Our companies
Our companies complement our position at the heart of the world's energy markets and facilitate the flow of energy from, into and across key markets, globally...


