Trading



Home  What we do  Trading
7m+ barrels of crude oil and products traded every dayWith 40 offices worldwide and a network of teams globally, we understand that every market is different. We work with our customers to identify and develop solutions which work best for them, helping them manage physical risk and optimise opportunities.
Our trading presence is underpinned by a complementary infrastructure: refining, storage, distribution and a marketing network across six continents. In all our physical operations we seek to work with partners which share our commitment to high international standards of operation. The infrastructure upon which we rely, from ships to jetties storage, is subject to our due diligence processes.
Explore trading


